description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Cooter purrs with a rating of 29, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 232, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Leverage for East, 1 for South, and Leverage for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
